{"about_the_game":"This is a side-scrolling  shoot 'em up game in which players fight by using both the close-range &quot;sword&quot; to slash enemies and shatter bullet barrages, and the far-reaching &quot;shooting&quot; style.<br>Players can learn techniques with various effects during the stage and can take on the mighty bosses in the style of their choice.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797420/extras/play.gif?t=1732288043\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2>The game features action with the sword, by wielding the sword,<br> Attack the enemy<br> Eliminate some bullets<br> Parry and nullify enemy melee attacks<br>and other actions are possible.<br><br>With the sword, power is accumulated and special techniques such as &quot;Iai&quot; and &quot;Ougi&quot; can be unleashed.<br>There are also challenging elements, such as reinforcement only during the stage with spiritual power obtained by defeating enemies, or permanent reinforcement with coins obtained by defeating bosses.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797420/extras/play2.gif?t=1732288043\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2>The time is turbulent.<br>Two divine swords, Kuroyuri and Shiroyuri, were dedicated deep in the mountains of Kyoto.<br>Their powerful power was only there to keep the demons and evil spirits from doing evil.<br><br>One day, a large thunderbolt destroyed the shrine and the sheath where the sword was located.<br>When left unarmed, the sword's power waned and it could not glare at the enemy.<br>They took the form of a person on one side and a sword on the other, and when fighting the enemy, they kept the sword inside their bodies. <br>Their journey to defeat the monsters and demons that abound in the world and to obtain a new sheath begins.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Awakening the sword","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity